sql:
SELECT model_name, MAX(model_version) AS latest_version
FROM models
GROUP BY model_name;

external_knowledge:
- "bustling" and "at the heart of frequent interactions" are metaphors for high user engagement and access frequency;
- "visited more than a dozen times" refers to having more than 10 access logs associated with the model;
- "thrive in such popularity" metaphorically describes models that have achieved significant user interaction and are thus considered successful or popular.
